To use this module:

1) Place the WX-RADAR-CONKY directory in the USER Module directory:
     - /ARCOS-DATA/QRV/CALLSIGN/arcos-linux-modules/USER

2) Place the 10_WX-RADAR-CONKY.sh script in the USER Module directory, as well.
     - One level up from where it is now.

3) Open the 10_WX-RADAR-CONKY.sh script in a text editor:
     - Modify the NWS_STATION and SIZE variables to suit your preferences.
     - Save the changes.

Notes:
The module will be active on the next reboot or re-run of Station Setup.

To deactivate the module, place the 00_WX-RADAR-CONKY.sh script back inside the WX-RADAR-CONKY directory and reboot.

In multi-user installations, WX-RADAR-CONKY will remain configured for a previous user, if the next user does not also use this module.
